Recently, a twitter user who goes by the name “Great Agha” uploaded the photo of a baby who was watching “The Morning Show” on Arise News and this spurred reactions from Twitter users.

Peter Obi, the presidential candidate for Labour party was interviewed on Arise News where he shared ways to move the country forward and addressed a whole lot of things while making revelations.
Then the twitter user In his post shared a photo of a little girl watching the interview. He captioned the photo; “When H.E Peter Obi is talking about you future, you have to pay attention”.
This spurred reactions from a number of twitter users, mostly positive ones like; one said we’re fighting because of the innocent ones like this, another said that not even cartoon network can distract you from a moment like this.
However, a few reactions were negative as one said; “Imagine, the innocent baby does not know the man is lying”.
